about_host:
We have stayed in so many wonderful AirBnBs around the world, we thought we would join the community. Local knowledge makes such a difference when you're traveling. We look forward to greeting you and pointing you in the right direction for your visit. Favorite mottos;
 (Website hidden by Airbnb) "Work hard. Play hard. Make a difference."
 (Website hidden by Airbnb) "Choose what you want, and pay for it."

// Couple from Leipzig, Germany now living in amazing Chicago because we felt it was time for a change of scenery //

We love traveling and meeting people from all over the world while staying in airbnb places. When at home, we like to do the same - this is why we share our apartment and the things we love about Chicago with you - so you can have an amazing time here.

We love interior design, music, cooking and eating, pastels colors, hyenas and hummus.
